  <title>Pregled nekoliko upravitelja prozorima</title>

  <p>Ovo je popis nekoliko dostupnih upravitelja prozorima.</p>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Marco</title>
    <p>Marco je uobičajeni upravitelj prozorima za MATE radno okruženje. Vrlo je stabilan i pouzdan. Može se pokrenuti bez kompostiranja.</p>
    <p>If Marco is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install marco</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Metacity</title>
    <p>Metacity je uobičajeni upravitelj prozorima za GNOME 2 radno okruženje. Vrlo je stabilan i pouzdan. Može se pokrenuti bez kompostiranja.</p>
    <p>If Metacity is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install metacity</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Mutter</title>
    <p>Mutter is the default window and compositing manager for the GNOME 3 desktop environment. It is very stable and very reliable.</p>
    <p>If Mutter is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install mutter</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Xfwm4</title>
    <p>Xfwm4 je uobičajeni upravitelj prozorima za Xfce radno okruženje. Vrlo je stabilan i pouzdan. Može se pokrenuti bez kompostiranja.</p>
    <p>If Xfwm4 is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install xfwm4</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Compiz</title>
    <p>Compiz je vrlo impresivan upravitelj prozorima, vrlo prilagodljiv s mnogo nevjerojatnih efekata i animacija. Zbog toga je manje pouzdan i stabilan.</p>
    <p>Compiz je standardno instaliran u Linux Mintu. Napomena: nije dostupan u LMDE.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Compton</title>
    <p>Compton je upravitelj prozorima. Može se koristiti u kombinaciji s upraviteljima prozorima poput Marco, Metacity ili Xfwm4. U Xfceu, koristeći Xfwm4+Compton je poznato da smanjuje kidanje zaslona.</p>
    <p>If Compton is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install compton</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="pros">
    <title>Openbox</title>
    <p>Openbox je brz upravitelj prozorima koji koristi malo resursa.</p>
    <p>If Openbox is not installed already, you can install it with <cmd>apt install openbox</cmd>.</p>
  </section>

